</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Monte_Alb%C3%A1n_archeological_site,_Oaxaca.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f2/Monte_Alb%C3%A1n_archeological_site,_Oaxaca.jpg/220px-Monte_Alb%C3%A1n_archeological_site,_Oaxaca.jpg" width="220" height="165" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f2/Monte_Alb%C3%A1n_archeological_site%2C_Oaxaca.jpg/330px-Monte_Alb%C3%A1n_archeological_site%2C_Oaxaca.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f2/Monte_Alb%C3%A1n_archeological_site%2C_Oaxaca.jpg/440px-Monte_Alb%C3%A1n_archeological_site%2C_Oaxaca.jpg 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Monte_Alb%C3%A1n_archeological_site,_Oaxaca.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf9/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
