<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEMichael_Tomasello1999511-21"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEMichael_Tomasello1999511_21-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEMichael_Tomasello1999511_21-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFMichael_Tomasello1999">Michael Tomasello 1999</a>, p.&#160;511.</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-22"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">M. King and A Wilson 1975 "Evolution at two levels: in humans and chimpanzees" <i>Science</i> 188: 107–116</span></li>
