<ul>
<li class="nv-view"><a href="Template_Articles_of_the_Universal_Declaration_of_Human_Rights" title="Template:Articles of the Universal Declaration of Human Rights"><span title="View this template" style=";;background:none transparent;border:none;">v</span></a></li>
